<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>GraphTemplate_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`GraphTemplate`<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>Cython-implemented<sp/>component<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework,<sp/>designed<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>foundational<sp/>template<sp/>for<sp/>graph-based<sp/>data<sp/>structures.<sp/>Similar<sp/>to<sp/>`EventTemplate`,<sp/>it<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>high-performance<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>graph<sp/>object,<sp/>facilitating<sp/>efficient<sp/>graph<sp/>manipulation<sp/>and<sp/>access<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>Python<sp/>environment.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>intended<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>inherited<sp/>by<sp/>more<sp/>specialized<sp/>graph<sp/>implementations,<sp/>offering<sp/>common<sp/>functionalities<sp/>for<sp/>graph<sp/>indexing,<sp/>tree<sp/>association,<sp/>and<sp/>pre-selection<sp/>management.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>GraphTemplate_class<sp/>The<sp/>GraphTemplate<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`GraphTemplate`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>signifying<sp/>its<sp/>implementation<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>This<sp/>allows<sp/>for<sp/>direct<sp/>and<sp/>optimized<sp/>interaction<sp/>with<sp/>C++<sp/>objects<sp/>and<sp/>types.<sp/>It<sp/>encapsulates<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>(`self.ptr`)<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`graph_template`<sp/>object,<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>lifecycle<sp/>and<sp/>exposing<sp/>its<sp/>attributes<sp/>and<sp/>methods<sp/>to<sp/>Python.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
