<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>invoked<sp/>during<sp/>object<sp/>allocation.<sp/>If<sp/>the<sp/>instance<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>subclass<sp/>of<sp/>`GraphTemplate`,<sp/>it<sp/>returns<sp/>immediately.<sp/>Otherwise,<sp/>it<sp/>instantiates<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`graph_template`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>memory<sp/>address<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ptr`.</highlight></codeline>
