<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>standard<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer,<sp/>deliberately<sp/>left<sp/>empty<sp/>as<sp/>primary<sp/>initialization<sp/>is<sp/>handled<sp/>by<sp/>`__cinit__`<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>encapsulated<sp/>C++<sp/>object.</highlight></codeline>
